content.rendered:
Directed by Trivikram Srinivas.

Written by Sanjeev Tiwari.

Cast Pawan Kalyan(Abhishikth Bhargav). Keerthy Suresh(Sukumari). Anu Emmanuel(Suryakantham). Aadhi(Seetharam). Boman Irani(Govinda Bhargav ‘Vinda’). Kushboo(Indrani Bhargav). Rao Ramesh(Varma). Murli Sharma(Ajay Sharma). Sampath Raj(ACP). Tanikella Bharani(Appaji). Avantika(Daughter of Sampath Raj (as Avantika Vandanapu)). Sameer(Deenabandhu).Narra Srinivas.Srinivasa Reddy. Raghu Babu(Koteswar Rao). Ajay(Aditya Bandaru) . Vamsee Aloor(Mohan Bhargav). Rajsekhar Aningi(Company CEO). Darbha Appaji Ambarisha(Book Reader (Nakula Dharmam)). Pradeep Bajpai(Employee).Raja Chembolu. Indraja(Krishnaveni Bhargav).V. Jayaprakash. Maniissh Karma(Panjeet (as Manesh k Singh)). Vennela Kishore(Balasubramaniam). Krishna Kranthi(Employee). Chaitanya Krishna(Rohit). Pavitra Lokesh((as Pavithra Lokesh)). Abhishek Maharshi(Hacker).Adithya Menon.Aadukalam Naren. Duke Nwamerue(Dancer). Joana Nwamerue(Dancer).Pammi Sai. Lahari Shari(Sushmita). Parag Tyagi(Parag).Temper Vamsi

Language Telugu.

Producers S. Radha Krishna. P.D.V. Prasad.

Production Haarika & Hassine Creations.
